49:21.969 --> 49:24.369
Sweet and solid,

49:24.371 --> 49:26.371
funny without meaning to be.

49:26.373 --> 49:28.439
[ Phone rings ]

49:29.575 --> 49:31.608
<i>[ Ringing continues ]</i>
[ Barking ]

49:33.111 --> 49:35.111
Hello?
[ Lepelt ]
There are "poopies."

49:35.113 --> 49:38.114
"Poopies"?
At second chance
"poop" shelter.

49:38.116 --> 49:40.249
What?
Poor little
dalmatian "poopies."

49:40.251 --> 49:42.618
Dalmatians?
<i>Oui. </i> Second chance
"poopie" shelter.

49:42.620 --> 49:45.187
Hello?
Who is this? Hello?
[ Hangs up ]

49:45.189 --> 49:47.255
Hello? Hello?

49:49.659 --> 49:52.259
"Poopies"?
<i>Oui! </i> "Poopies"!

49:52.261 --> 49:54.961
Oh, puppies.
Mm-hmm.
<i>Oui. Voila.</i>

49:54.963 --> 49:59.098
You will find them
by the river at the foot
of the bridge.

49:59.100 --> 50:02.501
We'll pick them up
right away, monsieur.
[ Chuckles ] Bye.

50:02.503 --> 50:06.471
Box of abandoned puppies
just around the corner.

50:06.473 --> 50:09.073
Abandoned no more.

50:25.757 --> 50:28.023
[ Groans ]

50:35.331 --> 50:37.364
[ Whimpers ]
[ Knuckles cracking ]

50:39.634 --> 50:42.401
<i>Oh, blimey!</i>
<i>The coppers!</i>

50:43.771 --> 50:46.104
<i>[ Radio: Dispatcher ]</i>
<i>Forensics is on its way.</i>
<i>Over.</i>

50:46.106 --> 50:48.573
Don't panic, Kevin.
Let me handle this.

50:50.243 --> 50:52.276
Kevin Shepherd?
[ Waddlesworth ]
Yes, hello, guv.

50:52.278 --> 50:54.278
I'm Kevin Shepherd.
Waddlesworth!

50:54.280 --> 50:56.713
Sorry.
How can I help you,
officer?

50:57.782 --> 51:00.449
A warrant
to search the premises.

51:12.429 --> 51:15.029
You have expensive taste, sir.

51:15.031 --> 51:18.032
[ Whispers ]
Don't admit to anything.
What's all this about?

51:18.034 --> 51:22.069
<i>Sixteen dalmatian puppies</i>
<i>were reported stolen</i>
<i>last night.</i>

51:22.071 --> 51:24.604
<i>Sir.</i>

51:24.606 --> 51:26.638
You'll never guess.

51:30.243 --> 51:32.610
[ Whimpering ] Oh, no!

51:32.612 --> 51:34.311
Busted!

51:35.213 --> 51:37.713
<i>[ Whimpering ]</i>

51:55.232 --> 51:57.532
Oh, miss de vil.

51:57.534 --> 51:59.667
Ooh, I suppose I must.

51:59.669 --> 52:01.769
Disgusting creature!

52:06.208 --> 52:08.841
Oh! Ohh!

52:08.843 --> 52:11.743
Chloe, that helmet.
I'd rather have
my skull crushed.

52:11.745 --> 52:14.679
Cruella de vil,
you're under arrest.
[ Gasps ]

52:14.681 --> 52:18.516
Kevin Shepherd,
you're under arrest.
<i>[ Chloe ] Kevin!</i>

52:18.518 --> 52:21.418
Chloe.
Hello, miss Simon.

52:21.420 --> 52:24.554
Is he one
of your charges?
No, he's not the one.

52:24.556 --> 52:27.557
<i>She is!</i>
<i>Why suspect Kevin?</i>
<i>Caught him red-handed.</i>

52:27.559 --> 52:30.660
And he's got a record
for dognapping.

52:30.662 --> 52:33.696
- Mmm.
- I can explain.

52:33.698 --> 52:37.566
- You can explain
where you were last night.
- He was home kissing her. Oh!

52:37.568 --> 52:40.335
<i>[ Kevin ]</i>
<i>I was out.</i>
<i>Out?</i>

52:40.337 --> 52:42.837
- Out.
- I think we've established
he was out.

52:42.839 --> 52:47.307
- Right, let's discuss this
at the station.
- He was out... with me.

52:48.443 --> 52:52.244
<i>Found this, sir...</i>
<i>list of addresses.</i>

52:52.246 --> 52:54.713
All the houses that have
had dalmatians stolen.

52:56.683 --> 52:59.717
Chloe, you can't
possibly believe...
this is crazy!

52:59.719 --> 53:03.120
<i>I'm being set up.</i>
Here's the box of puppies
you asked us to...

53:03.122 --> 53:05.388
whatever it is,
I didn't do it.
<i>No.</i>

53:05.390 --> 53:09.725
I sent Ewan to pick up those.
There was a phone call and...

53:09.727 --> 53:12.861
- oops.
<i>- [ Kevin chuckling ]</i>

53:12.863 --> 53:16.231
<i>This is crazy.</i>
<i>Why would I steal</i>
<i>dalmatians?</i>

53:16.233 --> 53:19.300
<i>Hmm?</i>
<i>What possible motive</i>
<i>could I have to want to...</i>

53:19.302 --> 53:22.703
- the judge's order.
- What?

53:22.705 --> 53:25.238
Oh, Kevin, how could you?

53:25.240 --> 53:28.174
<i>- All this for money?</i>
- What?

53:28.176 --> 53:30.809
Just like you said
at the restaurant.

53:30.811 --> 53:35.313
<i>Would somebody</i>
<i>kindly acquaint me</i>
<i>with the facts?</i>

53:35.315 --> 53:40.450
If I'm caught stealing puppies,
my entire fortune goes to him.

53:40.452 --> 53:42.452
Would that be a motive?

53:42.454 --> 53:44.921
<i>[ Thunder rumbling ]</i>

53:46.157 --> 53:48.390
<i>[ Man talking on police radio ]</i>

53:48.392 --> 53:51.726
I'm innocent,
I tell you!
Innocent!

53:51.728 --> 53:54.228
Couldn't tear them
apart, sir.
Ah, never mind.

53:54.230 --> 53:57.664
Just goes to show,
a dog will love anyone.

53:57.666 --> 54:01.901
<i>Inspector Armstrong!</i>
<i>Oh, inspector, thank you.</i>

54:01.903 --> 54:04.503
You and your men
do such a wonderful job...

54:04.505 --> 54:06.872
<i>Protecting the weak</i>
<i>and the innocent.</i>

54:06.874 --> 54:09.908
<i>Oh, thank you very much.</i>
<i>And I must say,</i>
<i>miss de vil,</i>

54:09.910 --> 54:13.645
you are the most remarkable case
of rehabilitation I've known
in all my years on the force.

54:13.647 --> 54:16.314
Thank you so much.
Bye-bye.

54:16.316 --> 54:18.749
Good-bye.
[ Chuckling ]

54:26.925 --> 54:28.925
[ Cackling ]

54:28.927 --> 54:32.194
<i>[ Cackling continues ]</i>

54:37.800 --> 54:40.333
Don't be hard
on yourself, dear.

54:40.335 --> 54:42.968
We were both fooled.

54:42.970 --> 54:45.403
I'm sorry, miss de vil.

54:45.405 --> 54:48.305
I had no idea
that Kevin was a...

54:48.307 --> 54:50.273
that I let myself trust him.

54:50.275 --> 54:53.976
Oh, this is all so dreadful.
You need distraction, darling.

54:53.978 --> 54:57.713
I'm having a few friends
'round for dinner tonight
with their dogs.

54:57.715 --> 55:00.215
Why don't you and yours
join us?

55:00.217 --> 55:03.218
Adults only, of course.
Oh, do come.

55:03.220 --> 55:07.355
Remember, darling,
we have the doggies
to live for.

55:07.357 --> 55:09.757
<i>[ Thunder rumbling ]</i>

55:09.759 --> 55:11.791
Smashing.

55:14.896 --> 55:17.363
<i>¶¶ [ Piano ]</i>
<i>[ Lepelt ]</i>
<i>a party?</i>

55:17.365 --> 55:21.867
I was hoping we would
dine alone tonight.

55:21.869 --> 55:25.503
- I can't be seen dining
with a furrier, you fool.
- You fool!

55:25.505 --> 55:29.507
Grr!
In fact, you shouldn't
even be here at all.

55:29.509 --> 55:32.476
Why do you keep
that "job odd" man
about the place?

55:32.478 --> 55:35.245
Are you jealous,
Jean-Pierre?
Jealous? Of him?

55:35.247 --> 55:37.547
Poo!
What can he do for you?

55:37.549 --> 55:39.549
Steal puppies.
Poo!

55:39.551 --> 55:42.351
Like taking the baby
from the candy.
Oh, just like.

55:42.353 --> 55:44.419
Well, now's your chance
to impress me.

55:44.421 --> 55:47.255
I've saved the last three
for you.
Me?

55:47.257 --> 55:50.925
Three very special puppies.
The owner will be out.

55:50.927 --> 55:55.562
But,<i> cherie...</i>
faint heart never won
fair lady, Jean-Pierre.

55:55.564 --> 55:59.866
[ Giggling ]
The keys, my little c-cabbage.

56:17.652 --> 56:19.718
Dipstick.

56:28.895 --> 56:32.796
Chloe, darling!
Dipstick.

56:32.798 --> 56:34.798
How kind of you to come.

56:34.800 --> 56:36.966
[ Growls, barks ] <i>Oh!</i>

56:36.968 --> 56:39.468
We're not still holding
a grudge, are we?

56:39.470 --> 56:42.404
[ Growling ]
Dipstick,
be polite.

56:42.406 --> 56:45.673
<i>I'm so pleased</i>
<i>you're here, darling.</i>

56:45.675 --> 56:47.708
Come with me.

56:50.079 --> 56:52.379
<i>Now, tell me.</i>

56:52.381 --> 56:55.348
<i>Your little spotted puppies...</i>

56:55.350 --> 56:57.450
Are snug and safe at home?

56:57.452 --> 57:00.619
Yes, they're
with dottie.
Oh, with mummy!

57:00.621 --> 57:02.721
Yes.
How dear.

57:03.924 --> 57:07.558
It's such a relief
to have the bad man
in jail.

57:07.560 --> 57:11.495
[ Snoring ]
<i>If puppies can't be safe</i>
<i>in this world, who can?</i>

57:11.497 --> 57:14.530
[ Snoring, squawking ]

57:17.768 --> 57:20.435
<i>[ Cruella ] Dinner is served.</i>

57:20.437 --> 57:23.037
<i>Alonzo?</i>
[ Chair legs
scraping floor ]

57:24.707 --> 57:28.142
Take our guests of honor
to their places.

57:28.144 --> 57:31.211
I've a special surprise
planned for you, my dear.

57:37.919 --> 57:40.552
[ Whispering ]
<i>[ Utensil tapping ]</i>

57:44.124 --> 57:47.959
Tonight our dogs
join us at table...

57:47.961 --> 57:52.529
<i>So we can show our appreciation</i>
<i>to a magnificent species.</i>

57:52.531 --> 57:54.631
<i>My past...</i>

57:54.633 --> 57:56.699
<i>Has been riddled with mistakes.</i>

57:56.701 --> 57:59.068
I pray someday to be forgiven.

57:59.070 --> 58:01.470
- [ Growls ]
- Shh.

58:01.472 --> 58:06.074
But tonight I will begin
to set things right.

58:06.076 --> 58:08.209
From tonight...

58:08.211 --> 58:10.944
We'll be closer than ever.

58:13.214 --> 58:16.949
- To the dogs.
- To the dogs!

58:21.955 --> 58:24.555
[ All gasping ]

58:24.557 --> 58:27.724
<i>[ Cruella clapping ]</i>

58:27.726 --> 58:31.928
- [ Whines ]
- "Bone"<i> appetit!</i>

58:33.031 --> 58:36.165
<i>- Please eat! Eat!</i>
- [ Snarling ]

58:42.873 --> 58:46.107
Dipstick.
Do you want mine?

58:46.109 --> 58:48.843
- [ Whines ]
- [ Barks ]

58:48.845 --> 58:52.746
<i>[ Gagging ]</i>

58:52.748 --> 58:54.647
[ Clears throat ]

58:58.786 --> 59:01.253
<i>- [ Guests murmuring ]</i>
- Ugh!

59:08.795 --> 59:11.262
Whee!

59:11.264 --> 59:13.697
<i>Whee!</i>
<i>[ Laughing continues ]</i>

59:15.934 --> 59:18.901
- Oh, my... oh!
- [ Shouts ]

59:18.903 --> 59:20.702
Everyone, eat!

59:34.250 --> 59:37.751
Where's dipstick?
Dipstick!

59:37.753 --> 59:40.086
Dipstick!

1:00:00.774 --> 1:00:04.642
[ Growling ]

1:00:04.644 --> 1:00:06.677
[ Barks ]

1:01:02.000 --> 1:01:04.833
[ Panting ]

1:01:08.171 --> 1:01:12.373
[ Growls, gurgling ]

1:01:15.378 --> 1:01:18.145
Oh!
[ Muttering ]

1:01:19.248 --> 1:01:22.182
Oh. Oh.

1:01:22.184 --> 1:01:24.784
[ Grunting ]

1:01:24.786 --> 1:01:27.019
[ Angry blubbering ]

1:01:40.667 --> 1:01:44.235
Ahh,<i> bonsoir,</i> my little ones.

1:01:44.237 --> 1:01:46.804
<i>I am the great lepelt,</i>

1:01:46.806 --> 1:01:51.808
<i>and you are...</i>
<i>how do you say...</i>
<i>dog meat.</i>

1:01:51.810 --> 1:01:54.410
<i>[ Growling, barks ]</i>

1:01:54.412 --> 1:01:57.279
Oh!
Nice. Nice, doggy.

1:01:58.382 --> 1:02:02.283
Dog nice!
Aaaah! Nice!

1:02:02.285 --> 1:02:04.752
[ Blubbering ]

1:02:04.754 --> 1:02:07.221
[ Barking ] Quiet!

1:02:08.290 --> 1:02:10.323
Shh. Nice doggy.

1:02:10.325 --> 1:02:12.024
<i>Be quiet!</i>

1:02:12.026 --> 1:02:15.694
<i>Be nice.</i>
<i>[ Groans ]</i>

1:02:15.696 --> 1:02:17.696
Naah!

1:02:23.903 --> 1:02:27.304
<i>[ Growling ]</i>

1:02:27.306 --> 1:02:29.239
[ Yipping ]

1:02:30.775 --> 1:02:32.975
Hee-hee! Hee-hee!

1:02:42.919 --> 1:02:46.854
Three puppies, she said, hmm?

1:02:46.856 --> 1:02:48.956
Yaah!

1:02:48.958 --> 1:02:52.159
[ Whimpers, barking ]

1:02:52.161 --> 1:02:54.728
Well.
[ Laughing ]

1:03:07.041 --> 1:03:10.242
Aaah! Aaaah!

1:03:10.244 --> 1:03:13.144
[ Grunting ] Oh!

1:03:13.146 --> 1:03:18.248
[ Barking ]

1:03:19.985 --> 1:03:22.451
<i>[ Barking continues ]</i>

1:03:24.788 --> 1:03:28.156
[ Howls ]

1:03:45.274 --> 1:03:49.142
[ Barking, howling ]

1:03:56.184 --> 1:03:59.351
<i>[ Dogs barking ]</i> [ Yipping ]

1:04:01.054 --> 1:04:03.554
[ Bell dinging ]

1:04:03.556 --> 1:04:06.523
[ Barking ]

1:04:12.797 --> 1:04:14.830
[ Barking ]

1:04:16.567 --> 1:04:18.800
[ Amplified barking ]

1:04:30.379 --> 1:04:33.313
Surprise!
[ Cackling ]

1:04:33.315 --> 1:04:36.249
Earlier than I planned,
but<i> c'est LA vie.</i>

1:04:36.251 --> 1:04:39.418
- I hereby revoke
your probation.
- And I hereby lock you up.

1:04:39.420 --> 1:04:43.188
With St. Kevin of assisi
in the clink,
it just wouldn't do...

1:04:43.190 --> 1:04:46.191
If three more puppies
were reported missing.

1:04:46.193 --> 1:04:48.526
- Three more?
- Good-bye, my dear.

1:04:48.528 --> 1:04:50.427
- [ Cackling ]
- No!

1:04:50.429 --> 1:04:54.297
<i>I'll think of you</i>
<i>every time I wear</i>
<i>your sweet little doggies!</i>

1:04:54.299 --> 1:04:56.599
No!
<i>[ Cackling continues ]</i>

1:04:56.601 --> 1:04:59.201
Stop!

1:05:00.904 --> 1:05:02.970
<i>[ Barking ]</i>

1:05:11.179 --> 1:05:15.080
[ Sinister laughing ]
Ooh, not bad.

1:05:15.082 --> 1:05:17.449
The English
can do the knitwear.

1:05:19.386 --> 1:05:23.121
<i>[ Barking ]</i> [ Grunts ]

1:05:33.198 --> 1:05:35.263
<i>[ Barking ]</i>

1:05:37.634 --> 1:05:40.267
Shh! Be quiet!

1:05:52.147 --> 1:05:54.180
[ Horn honking ]

1:05:54.182 --> 1:05:57.950
[ Snores ] Ooh!

1:05:57.952 --> 1:06:00.452
Hey, what's that?
Listen. Hey.

1:06:00.454 --> 1:06:03.588
<i>Do you hear that?</i>
What? What is it?

1:06:03.590 --> 1:06:07.458
Uh, best I can make out,
they're all yappin'
about "tubble."

1:06:07.460 --> 1:06:10.661
Tubble? Oh, trouble.
Must be puppies talking.

1:06:10.663 --> 1:06:12.663
Listen. Hey, wait.
There's more.

1:06:12.665 --> 1:06:17.433
Uh, "widdle ones"?
"Bad man gwab widdle ones.

1:06:17.435 --> 1:06:19.501
Twee potted doggies."

1:06:19.503 --> 1:06:22.670
Potted?
Twee widdle potted...

1:06:23.973 --> 1:06:27.273
bad man grabs three
little spotted doggies.

1:06:30.444 --> 1:06:32.944
Oh, my gosh.
Chloe's dogs.

1:06:41.553 --> 1:06:45.288
[ Growling ]

1:06:53.163 --> 1:06:55.196
Aah!

1:07:11.080 --> 1:07:13.680
Aaaah!

1:07:13.682 --> 1:07:16.382
Oh! Aah! Aah!
Aah! Aah!

1:07:24.091 --> 1:07:27.125
[ Moans ]

1:07:28.161 --> 1:07:31.562
<i>The puppies!</i>
<i>[ Gasps ]</i>

1:07:31.564 --> 1:07:34.698
Thank you, Fluffy!

1:07:34.700 --> 1:07:37.467
[ Waddlesworth ]
¶ go to sleep ¶

1:07:37.469 --> 1:07:40.603
<i>¶ go to sleep ¶</i>

1:07:40.605 --> 1:07:46.041
¶ go to sleep little guardie ¶¶

1:07:46.043 --> 1:07:48.076
[ sighs ]

1:07:53.616 --> 1:07:57.117
Dog, James dog.

1:07:59.588 --> 1:08:01.487
Aah!

1:08:02.990 --> 1:08:05.390
¶ Go back to sleep ¶

1:08:05.392 --> 1:08:09.593
<i>¶ go back to sleep</i>
<i>stupid guardie ¶¶</i>

1:08:09.595 --> 1:08:11.394
[ sighs ]

1:08:22.373 --> 1:08:24.439
Taxi!

1:08:27.577 --> 1:08:31.412
St. John's mews, please.
You know, I could get
five to ten for this.

1:08:31.414 --> 1:08:34.214
That's 35 to 70 in dog years.

1:08:34.216 --> 1:08:36.282
Ow!

1:08:38.286 --> 1:08:40.719
<i>[ Quiet sobbing ]</i>

1:09:04.077 --> 1:09:06.110
They've gone.

1:09:17.556 --> 1:09:20.189
Where are they?
Calm down,
calm down.

1:09:20.191 --> 1:09:23.125
<i>[ Growls, barks ]</i>

1:09:23.127 --> 1:09:25.393
- Whoa!
- Aah!

1:09:26.829 --> 1:09:30.463
Hoo! Aaah!

1:09:38.707 --> 1:09:41.607
I'm so sorry.
I should have trusted you.

1:09:41.609 --> 1:09:44.209
No, I should never
have trusted Cruella.

1:09:44.211 --> 1:09:46.177
With my police record...
it doesn't matter.

1:09:46.179 --> 1:09:48.244
Yes, it does matter.

1:09:50.414 --> 1:09:52.547
Look,

1:09:52.549 --> 1:09:56.551
I broke into the lab
and freed those dogs.

1:09:56.553 --> 1:09:59.487
They were being used
for experiments.

1:10:00.790 --> 1:10:04.424
That was your
dognapping conviction?

1:10:04.426 --> 1:10:06.692
Yes.

1:10:06.694 --> 1:10:09.294
That's all?
Yes.

1:10:40.994 --> 1:10:43.527
What's this?

1:10:43.529 --> 1:10:45.729
"The<i> orient-express."</i>

1:10:48.433 --> 1:10:50.599
Paris.
[ Barks ]

1:10:52.002 --> 1:10:54.736
They're going to Paris!
Come on!

1:10:56.573 --> 1:10:58.940
<i>[ Cruella ]</i>
<i>Oh, Jean-Pierre,</i>
<i>you've outdone yourself.</i>

1:10:58.942 --> 1:11:02.009
I am the Napoleon of the fur,
and you are my...

1:11:02.011 --> 1:11:04.711
Waterloo?
My Josephine.
Together we'll...

1:11:04.713 --> 1:11:06.679
aaah! A rat!

1:11:07.715 --> 1:11:10.782
I need spotted puppies,
you idiot!

1:11:10.784 --> 1:11:13.317
But it is not a rat.
I know rats!

1:11:13.319 --> 1:11:15.919
It's a "poopie."
<i>Alonzo!</i>

1:11:15.921 --> 1:11:18.454
Yes.
Find the rat
and kill it.

1:11:18.456 --> 1:11:21.390
- Lepelt and I will be
on the<i> orient-express.</i>
- K-kill?

1:11:21.392 --> 1:11:24.960
The last time
I underestimated a puppy,
I wound up in the pokey!

1:11:24.962 --> 1:11:27.429
Go! Go!
Why not him?

1:11:27.431 --> 1:11:30.665
Oh! Yes, I see.
Thank you.

1:11:45.448 --> 1:11:48.315
Ahh.

1:11:48.317 --> 1:11:50.717
There.

1:11:50.719 --> 1:11:53.285
<i>[ Barking, whining ]</i>

1:11:56.423 --> 1:11:59.490
<i>[ Barking continues ]</i>

1:12:04.563 --> 1:12:06.763
Yaah!

1:12:06.765 --> 1:12:09.365
[ Grunting ]

1:12:09.367 --> 1:12:11.433
<i>[ Dog yelping ]</i>

1:12:11.435 --> 1:12:14.068
Oh, oh. Ohh!

1:12:14.070 --> 1:12:16.669
Ohh-ohh-ohh-ohh!

1:12:19.373 --> 1:12:21.406
[ Gasps ]

1:12:23.676 --> 1:12:26.843
Excuse me.
The<i> orient-express?</i>
Platform nine.

1:12:29.848 --> 1:12:32.548
Paris!
City of<i> l'amour!</i>
Of<i> LA mode!</i>

1:12:32.550 --> 1:12:35.050
Of lepelt!
[ Both cackling ]

1:12:39.522 --> 1:12:43.824
<i>[ Barking ]</i>

1:12:43.826 --> 1:12:46.426
[ Barking, whining ]

1:12:52.033 --> 1:12:54.732
[ Whimpering ]

1:12:57.470 --> 1:13:01.738
[ Grunts ]
Lepelt, with his slippery
frenchman ways.

1:13:01.740 --> 1:13:05.441
She'll see. She'll see
that I'm the loyal one.

1:13:07.011 --> 1:13:10.412
<i>Alonzo.</i>
<i>Oh, joy.</i>
Le petit homme.

1:13:10.414 --> 1:13:12.746
- You took care of the rat?
<i>- [ Ice cubes rattle ]</i>

1:13:14.750 --> 1:13:16.850
You will never...

1:13:16.852 --> 1:13:20.086
See it... again.

1:13:21.656 --> 1:13:23.688
<i>[ Bell dinging ]</i>

1:13:26.693 --> 1:13:28.726
[ Kevin ]
This isn't the<i> orient-express.</i>

1:13:28.728 --> 1:13:31.628
[ Waddlesworth ]
We're on the wrong platform!
There she is!

1:13:34.432 --> 1:13:36.498
Come on.

1:13:38.802 --> 1:13:42.003
Oddball!

1:13:43.973 --> 1:13:46.974
<i>Oh, no, I can't look!</i>
<i>She'll be killed!</i>

1:13:46.976 --> 1:13:51.511
[ Yipping ]

1:13:52.614 --> 1:13:54.747
Somebody do something!

1:13:54.749 --> 1:13:58.150
Oh, what am I doing?
Help! Help!

1:13:58.152 --> 1:14:00.085
Your wings!
Flap your wings!

1:14:00.087 --> 1:14:04.522
Flap wings? Oh!
Where did these come from?

1:14:04.524 --> 1:14:07.758
Blimey, they work!
I can fly!

1:14:07.760 --> 1:14:10.426
<i>Dogs can fly!</i>

1:14:12.396 --> 1:14:14.162
[ Barks ]

1:14:19.101 --> 1:14:20.967
Whee-yah!

1:14:20.969 --> 1:14:24.170
I just realized
I'm not a rottweiler
at all!

1:14:24.172 --> 1:14:26.405
I'm a retriever.

1:14:26.407 --> 1:14:28.640
[ Yips ] <i>[ Barking ]</i>

1:14:28.642 --> 1:14:31.509
[ Whining ]

1:14:35.615 --> 1:14:38.081
<i>[ Clattering ]</i>

1:14:41.719 --> 1:14:43.685
Where are we going?
Paris!

1:14:43.687 --> 1:14:45.848
We've missed the train!
Then we'll catch
the next one!

1:14:48.057 --> 1:14:51.124
You think he saw us?
We better... we better hide.

1:14:51.126 --> 1:14:53.159
<i>But where?</i>

1:14:55.129 --> 1:14:58.563
What?
Bad wady's cow?
<i>[ Barking ]</i>

1:14:58.565 --> 1:15:01.032
Oh, good idea, spotty.

1:15:02.435 --> 1:15:07.171
[ Whistle blowing ]

1:15:15.814 --> 1:15:18.113
<i>Vive LA Paris!</i>
Careful now.

1:15:20.851 --> 1:15:22.917
Careful. Careful.

1:15:23.953 --> 1:15:26.486
Uh, careful!

1:15:26.488 --> 1:15:29.522
Mustn't harm
the "poopies."
[ Chuckles ]

1:15:29.524 --> 1:15:33.892
[ Tires screeching ]

1:15:33.894 --> 1:15:37.629
[ Horn honking ]

1:15:39.232 --> 1:15:44.534
The p-poopieman
gets to ride in the c-car.

1:15:44.536 --> 1:15:47.236
Is Alonzo keeping up?

1:15:47.238 --> 1:15:49.605
The little man is too slow.

1:15:49.607 --> 1:15:53.875
This traffic is too slow.
The French are<i> useless</i>
behind the wheel!

1:15:53.877 --> 1:15:56.844
[ Cruella laughing ]

1:15:58.180 --> 1:16:00.580
<i>[ Lepelt ]</i>
<i>Aah! You're going</i>
<i>the wrong way!</i>

1:16:00.582 --> 1:16:03.115
They're going
the wrong way!
<i>[ Horn honking ]</i>

1:16:03.117 --> 1:16:06.218
<i>We're going to die!</i>

1:16:06.220 --> 1:16:08.186
[ Horn honks ]

1:16:08.188 --> 1:16:10.254
[ Whimpering ]

1:16:13.559 --> 1:16:15.692
[ Screams ]
Shut up, Jean-Pierre!

1:16:15.694 --> 1:16:17.927
- [ Bicycle bell dings ]
<i>- [ Tires screech ]</i>

1:16:19.063 --> 1:16:21.830
<i>Jean-Pierre,</i>
<i>our next challenge:</i>

1:16:21.832 --> 1:16:24.766
<i>Reinventing the poodle skirt.</i>

1:16:26.703 --> 1:16:29.069
[ Woman complaining in French ]

1:16:31.807 --> 1:16:34.774
<i>[ Dogs barking ]</i>

1:16:43.985 --> 1:16:47.986
Nothing.
Nobody saw anything.
Oh!

1:16:50.991 --> 1:16:53.791
<i>[ Dog barking in distance ]</i>

1:16:56.695 --> 1:17:00.029
I didn't know you spoke French.

1:17:00.031 --> 1:17:02.564
[ Horns honking ]

1:17:02.566 --> 1:17:05.066
<i>Come on! Come on!</i>

1:17:05.068 --> 1:17:07.068
Taxi, stop!

1:17:07.070 --> 1:17:09.136
[ Horn honks ]

1:17:20.081 --> 1:17:22.548
So what did they say?

1:17:22.550 --> 1:17:25.117
[ Barking ] Follow<i> les chiens.</i>

1:17:35.662 --> 1:17:37.561
[ Waddlesworth ]
It's spooky, all right,

1:17:37.563 --> 1:17:41.064
but you'd have to be
a sniveling, whimpering,
cowardly little chihuahua...

1:17:41.066 --> 1:17:44.000
Not to barge right
in there and take charge
of the situation...

1:17:44.002 --> 1:17:46.135
With no hesitation at all.

1:17:47.872 --> 1:17:49.938
After you, then.

1:18:00.983 --> 1:18:03.283
Ohh, I'm gonna regret this.

1:18:14.962 --> 1:18:19.898
<i>What do you look at?</i>
<i>Work! Work!</i>

1:18:24.170 --> 1:18:26.837
Illegal immigrants?
Of course.

1:18:26.839 --> 1:18:29.706
Hmm. How much?

1:18:30.842 --> 1:18:33.309
Fifty francs a week.
Oh.
[ Chuckles ]

1:18:33.311 --> 1:18:35.811
That's not much.

1:18:35.813 --> 1:18:38.313
It's all they can afford.

1:18:38.315 --> 1:18:41.849
Sure hope you know
where you're going, pup.

1:18:41.851 --> 1:18:46.019
- Bingo.
- [ Barking ]

1:18:46.021 --> 1:18:49.689
Don't worry, oddball.
I'll have 'em out
in a jiffy.

1:18:49.691 --> 1:18:51.757
[ Grunts ]

1:18:56.164 --> 1:18:59.731
<i>Hmm. Tastes like chicken.</i>

1:19:02.769 --> 1:19:05.936
[ Panting ]

1:19:05.938 --> 1:19:08.004
[ Whimpering ]

1:19:09.240 --> 1:19:11.306
Ooh.

1:19:13.043 --> 1:19:16.911
It's no good
looking at me
like that.

1:19:16.913 --> 1:19:19.313
It won't do any good, you know.

1:19:20.883 --> 1:19:23.750
Sorry.

1:19:26.821 --> 1:19:30.055
<i>[ Hatch closing ]</i>

1:19:38.231 --> 1:19:40.764
<i>[ Door closes ]</i>
[ Whispers ]
Okay.

1:19:56.113 --> 1:19:59.080
Go right through.

1:19:59.082 --> 1:20:01.348
Did you hear something?

1:20:01.350 --> 1:20:04.017
It's just your little man
outside.

1:20:07.922 --> 1:20:11.790
[ Barking ]
Shh, shh, shh,
shh, shh!

1:20:14.828 --> 1:20:18.095
Hey, I thought I told you
to wait outside. Hey.

1:20:18.097 --> 1:20:22.331
I know, but they
were worried. Oh!

1:20:24.168 --> 1:20:26.868
Hello!

1:20:26.870 --> 1:20:29.337
Hi!

1:20:29.339 --> 1:20:32.139
Okay, let's get them
out of here.

1:20:33.308 --> 1:20:36.442
Come on.
<i>[ Cruella ]</i>
<i>well, miss Houdini.</i>

1:20:37.545 --> 1:20:39.878
Aren't you in a tight spot?

1:20:41.281 --> 1:20:44.248
Ooh, what fun
to get away with murder!

1:20:44.250 --> 1:20:46.350
Ta-ta!
[ Cackling ]

1:20:46.352 --> 1:20:49.319
<i>[ Cackling continues ]</i>

1:20:49.321 --> 1:20:52.355
I'm really beginning
to dislike that woman.

1:20:59.096 --> 1:21:01.996
There's got to be a way
out of here.

1:21:12.407 --> 1:21:15.608
Hello, nice bird.
Aah!
Aah!

1:21:15.610 --> 1:21:17.910
Waddlesworth!
Is oddball with you?

1:21:17.912 --> 1:21:21.179
You bet she's here.
She's commando leader.

1:21:21.181 --> 1:21:24.081
- Now, pass up the pups, quick.
- Okay.

1:21:24.083 --> 1:21:27.150
One. Have a seat.

1:21:29.120 --> 1:21:32.221
Two. Good, good.
Join the other one.

1:21:32.223 --> 1:21:35.224
<i>Come on, hurry up, hurry up.</i>

1:21:44.534 --> 1:21:47.501
<i>[ Sewing machine engines</i>
<i>whirring ]</i>

1:21:55.944 --> 1:21:59.578
One hundred. In a bunch.
Come on, in a bunch.

1:21:59.580 --> 1:22:03.214
One hundred and...
are you 100 or 101?

1:22:03.216 --> 1:22:06.450
Great. Now we have
to start all over again.
That's it.

1:22:13.125 --> 1:22:15.959
Bring me the "poopies"!

1:22:15.961 --> 1:22:17.894
Come on!

1:22:27.004 --> 1:22:29.204
This is my favorite part.

1:22:29.206 --> 1:22:31.673
The skinning?
Not the strangling?

1:22:31.675 --> 1:22:33.975
Ah, I like the strangling also.

1:22:33.977 --> 1:22:37.611
<i>The mark of a great furrier,</i>
<i>Alonzo, is that he does</i>
<i>his own strangling.</i>

1:22:37.613 --> 1:22:40.213
<i>Remember that.</i>
Thank you.

1:22:40.215 --> 1:22:42.215
Shh.

1:22:42.217 --> 1:22:44.584
[ Sniffing ]

1:22:46.087 --> 1:22:48.420
- Wha...
- [ Alonzo grunts ]

1:22:48.422 --> 1:22:52.657
Aaah!
It's the little rat!

1:22:52.659 --> 1:22:55.092
You lied to me.

1:22:55.094 --> 1:22:57.661
M-m-me?
Why should I...
ugh!

1:22:57.663 --> 1:23:01.464
Does she look dead to you?
Does she?

1:23:01.466 --> 1:23:05.266
You worm!
I'll kill her myself.

1:23:07.703 --> 1:23:10.103
You are a wormy little man.

1:23:17.378 --> 1:23:20.145
Oh!
[ Grunts ]

1:23:22.449 --> 1:23:24.715
Aaah!

1:23:30.255 --> 1:23:32.255
[ Growling ]

1:23:32.257 --> 1:23:34.290
[ Angry grunt ]

1:23:36.294 --> 1:23:39.061
Whoa!

1:23:39.063 --> 1:23:42.597
Oh! You're both idiots!

1:23:57.413 --> 1:23:59.479
<i>[ Lepelt laughing ]</i>

1:23:59.481 --> 1:24:02.348
[ Waddlesworth ]
Aah! Excuse me!

1:24:08.155 --> 1:24:10.989
Work!

1:24:22.435 --> 1:24:25.169
<i>Now I crush you, little man!</i>

1:24:26.305 --> 1:24:30.373
- [ Chloe ]
Aaah!
- [ Growling ]

1:24:30.375 --> 1:24:33.342
[ Workers chattering
excitedly ]

1:24:33.344 --> 1:24:36.078
Who's the little man now?

1:24:36.080 --> 1:24:39.081
[ Growling ]

1:24:39.083 --> 1:24:42.350
Aaah!

1:24:46.756 --> 1:24:51.291
[ Workers cheering, laughing ]

1:24:54.329 --> 1:24:56.562
[ Panting ]

1:24:58.732 --> 1:25:02.800
I'll wear you on my sleeve.

1:25:38.670 --> 1:25:42.204
<i>Here, puppy, puppy.</i>
<i>Puppy.</i>

1:25:42.206 --> 1:25:44.706
Sweet puppy.

1:25:46.543 --> 1:25:48.309
Uhh!

1:25:53.348 --> 1:25:55.815
[ Yipping ]

1:26:01.722 --> 1:26:04.689
[ Gasping ]

1:26:22.808 --> 1:26:25.809
Oh! Oh!

1:26:27.145 --> 1:26:31.780
- [ Alarm blaring ]
- [ Whistle blows ]

1:26:52.669 --> 1:26:57.504
<i>[ Buzzer buzzing ]</i>
[ Gasps ]
Oh, oh! No!

1:26:57.506 --> 1:26:59.905
Aah!

1:27:02.676 --> 1:27:05.643
Aaaah! Ugh.

1:27:09.881 --> 1:27:11.680
[ Clucking sound ]

1:27:17.487 --> 1:27:19.553
Oh! Oh!

1:27:29.698 --> 1:27:32.165
Oh. Aah!

1:27:57.625 --> 1:27:59.891
Oh! Aah, aah!

1:27:59.893 --> 1:28:02.827
Ohh! Aah! Aah!

1:28:02.829 --> 1:28:05.496
<i>[ Motor speeding up ]</i>

1:28:05.498 --> 1:28:10.334
Aaah! Aaah!

1:28:27.919 --> 1:28:30.519
Quickly!
To the bakery!
But can we trust him?

1:28:30.521 --> 1:28:33.989
Now is not the time
to count your change, Kevin.
Come on!

1:28:33.991 --> 1:28:36.224
She's after the puppies!

1:28:48.304 --> 1:28:50.604
[ Gasps ]

1:29:03.985 --> 1:29:06.918
<i>I've got you now,</i>
<i>you little rat!</i>

1:29:09.889 --> 1:29:11.889
[ Frustrated grunting ]

1:29:11.891 --> 1:29:13.924
<i>[ Buzzer buzzes ]</i> [ Cackling ]

1:29:25.637 --> 1:29:27.703
Oh.

1:29:29.373 --> 1:29:32.307
[ Cackling ]

1:29:34.344 --> 1:29:37.044
Without spots,
you're just not
worth the trouble.

1:29:37.046 --> 1:29:39.279
Chop, chop.

1:29:44.852 --> 1:29:47.585
<i>And now to my coat!</i>

1:29:50.323 --> 1:29:52.022
<i>[ Oddball barks ]</i>

1:29:56.028 --> 1:29:58.962
[ Screaming ]

1:30:17.615 --> 1:30:20.782
<i>[ Chloe ]</i>
<i>Domino! Little dipper!</i>

1:30:20.784 --> 1:30:23.951
Oddball!
Oddball?

1:30:23.953 --> 1:30:27.587
Where are you?
Come out, come out,
wherever you are!

1:30:34.629 --> 1:30:37.396
[ Bell dings ]

1:30:48.676 --> 1:30:51.076
[ Gasps ]

1:30:52.679 --> 1:30:54.912
Ahh!

1:31:36.889 --> 1:31:39.222
[ Blubbering ]

1:31:41.926 --> 1:31:43.926
<i>[ Low bark ]</i>

1:31:45.162 --> 1:31:48.163
Aaah-aah!

1:31:48.165 --> 1:31:50.832
Oh!

1:31:50.834 --> 1:31:53.034
And now for the topper.

1:31:53.036 --> 1:31:55.836
<i>You may now kick the bride.</i>

1:32:07.816 --> 1:32:10.883
[ Quiet moan ]

1:32:23.563 --> 1:32:28.065
<i>I'm ruined!</i>
<i>This is the fall</i>
<i>of</i> Maison lepelt.

1:32:28.067 --> 1:32:30.700
How do we get out
from this mess?

1:32:30.702 --> 1:32:33.202
Piece of cake.

1:32:53.890 --> 1:32:57.324
<i>Look out, everybody!</i>
<i>It's the bad lady's cow.</i>

1:32:57.326 --> 1:32:59.559
Oh, no.

1:33:10.804 --> 1:33:13.037
Hello, all.

1:33:13.039 --> 1:33:16.640
I've come from miss de vil's
solicitor, Mr. torte.

1:33:16.642 --> 1:33:20.243
I asked if I might
have the pleasure
of delivering this.

1:33:34.591 --> 1:33:37.825
- Eight million pounds?
- Yes!

1:33:37.827 --> 1:33:40.127
It's the judge's orders.
Eight million quid?

1:33:40.129 --> 1:33:42.162
Eight million pounds!
Eight million quid.

1:33:42.164 --> 1:33:44.764
It's for the dogs,
of course.
That's eight million.

1:33:44.766 --> 1:33:47.800
And for the best,
unless... unless she's
rehabilitated.

1:33:47.802 --> 1:33:49.802
<i>[ Chloe ] No, Alonzo.</i>

1:33:49.804 --> 1:33:52.671
Cruella will always be Cruella.

1:33:52.673 --> 1:33:54.673
Hope Springs eternal.

1:34:00.280 --> 1:34:03.046
<i>What's that puppy</i>
<i>doing up there?</i>

1:34:05.750 --> 1:34:07.683
No, oddball!
Oddball!

1:34:11.789 --> 1:34:14.389
Oh, oddball!
Ohh!

1:34:14.391 --> 1:34:18.025
What have you
been up to now?
What have you been doing?

1:34:18.027 --> 1:34:20.761
Hey! Hey.

1:34:20.763 --> 1:34:22.863
Ohh!

1:34:22.865 --> 1:34:24.865
Dirt.

1:34:24.867 --> 1:34:27.834
Kevin. Look.

1:34:27.836 --> 1:34:31.704
These won't come off.
She's got her spots.

1:34:32.640 --> 1:34:34.706
Oddball's got her spots!

1:34:34.708 --> 1:34:36.774
Look!

1:34:39.712 --> 1:34:41.778
[ Dogs barking ]

1:34:45.650 --> 1:34:50.019
<i>[ Waddlesworth ]</i>
<i>S-p-o-t-s!</i>

